    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Добавление картинок к вопросам]]></title>
    <link href="http://ggoha.github.io/blog/2016/12/13/dobavlieniie-kartinok-k-voprosam/"/>
    <updated>2016-12-13T19:30:58+03:00</updated>
    <id>http://ggoha.github.io/blog/2016/12/13/dobavlieniie-kartinok-k-voprosam</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Возникла потребность, к некоторым вопросам добавлять картинки. Реализуем такую возможность, паралельно решив некоторые проблемы с CSS.</p>

<!-- more -->


<h1>Связь изображений с вопросами</h1>

<p>Собственно генерируем новый загрузчик
<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rails generate uploader Picture</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
Добавляем столбец в модель
<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rails g migration add_picture_to_question picture:string
</span><span class='line'>rails db:migrate</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
Добавляем загрузчик в модель
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>question.rb </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='rb'><span class='line'><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Question</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">lt</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="no">ActiveRecord</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Base</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">mount_uploader</span> <span class="ss">:picture</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="no">PictureUploader</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">end</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
В форме загрузки для поддержки множественной загрузки добавляем multipart
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>tests/edit.html.slim </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='slim'><span class='line'><span class="p">=</span> <span class="n">form_tag</span> <span class="n">import_test_path</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="ss">multipart</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="kp">true</span> <span class="k">do</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="p">=</span> <span class="n">label_tag</span> <span class="ss">:pictures</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">Файлы</span> <span class="err">с</span> <span class="err">картинками</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="p">=</span> <span class="n">file_field_tag</span> <span class="ss">:pictures</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="ss">:multiple</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="kp">true</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">name</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">pictures</span><span class="o">[]&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="p">=</span> <span class="n">submit_tag</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">Импортировать</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
Так как картинки загружаются отдельно от вопросов, в качестве связи между ними будет выступать название картинки, которое совпадает с номером вопроса
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>test_controller.rb </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='rb'><span class='line'>  <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">import</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="vi">@test</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="no">Test</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">find</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">params</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="ss">:id</span><span class="o">]</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="vi">@test</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">import</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">params</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="ss">:pictures</span><span class="o">]</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">flash</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="ss">:success</span><span class="o">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">Вопросы</span> <span class="err">обновлены</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">render</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">edit</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">br</span><span class="o">/&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">end</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>test.rb </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='rb'><span class='line'>  <span class="k">if</span> <span class="o">!</span><span class="n">pictures_files</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">blank?</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">questions</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">questions</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">order</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="ss">:id</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">pictures_files</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">each</span> <span class="k">do</span> <span class="o">|</span><span class="n">picture</span><span class="o">|</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="c1">#переводим название картинки в номер вопроса с учетом, что начинается с 0</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="n">question_index</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="no">File</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">basename</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">picture</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">original_filename</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">*</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">to_i</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="n">questions</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="n">question_index</span><span class="o">].</span><span class="n">picture</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">picture</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="n">questions</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="n">question_index</span><span class="o">].</span><span class="n">save!</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">end</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">end</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
Таким образом мы добавили к нашим вопросам картинки, правда без возможности их удаления.</p>

<h1>Показ изображения</h1>

<p>Мы хотим получить нечто такое
<img src="/images/maket2.png">
Для этого
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>question.html.slim </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='slim'><span class='line'>  <span class="nc">.bordered</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nc">.description</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="p">=</span> <span class="n">image_tag</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="vi">@question</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">picture</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="ss">class</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">right</span> <span class="n">max100percent</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;)</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="p">=</span> <span class="vi">@question</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>style.css </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='css'><span class='line'><span class="nc">.right</span><span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">float</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="k">right</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="nc">.bordered</span><span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">border</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="m">9px</span> <span class="k">solid</span> <span class="m">#f2f2f2</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">overflow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="k">hidden</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="nc">.max100percent</span><span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">max-width</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="m">100%</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<strong>float: right</strong> нужен для обтекания картинки тестом.
<strong>overflow: hidden</strong> служит для правильной обработки изображения с <em>float</em> и свойства <em>border</em>
А <strong>max-width: 100%</strong> не позволяет даже большим изображениям занять больше размера, чем им предоставлено.
<p><div class='octopress-spoiler-block'><input type='checkbox' id='octopress-spoiler-block-14'       class='octopress-spoiler-block-head' checked/><label for='octopress-spoiler-block-14'>Другое решение         </label><div class='octopress-spoiler'>
В случае если максимальный размер поля для изображения известен, можно производить обработку изображения при загрузке и уменьшать ее до нужного размера
